milestones.description: Dennis Amiss has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (72) in an innings in ODIs for ENG, going past Dennis Amiss's 62
Dennis Amiss's 137 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for ENG), surpassing David Lloyd's 116
Chris Old has broken the record for most sixes (5) in ODIs for ENG, going past Tony Greig's 3
Dennis Amiss has become the top scorer for ENG in ODIs with 509 runs, going past Fletcher's 400
Madan Lal has become the top wicket-taker for IND in ODIs with 3 wickets, going past Bishan Bedi's 2
Karsan Ghavri has conceded the most runs in an innings (83) in ODIs for IND, going past Bishan Bedi's record of 68
Dennis Amiss has become the top scorer in ODIs with 509 runs, going past Fletcher's 400
Dennis Amiss's 137 is the highest individual score in ODIs, surpassing David Lloyd's 116
Dennis Amiss has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (72) in an innings in ODIs, going past Majid Khan's 70
Karsan Ghavri has conceded the most runs in an innings (83) in ODIs, going past Bevan Congdon's record of 77
England's 334 is the highest total in ODIs, surpassing England's 266
Dennis Amiss and Fletcher's 176-run partnership is the highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 143 between Fredericks and Alvin Kallicharran
Mike Denness and Chris Old's 89-run partnership is the highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 59 between Fletcher and Tony Greig
Syed Abid Ali has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for IND, going past Engineer
Dennis Amiss and Fletcher's 176-run partnership is ENG's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 125 between Fletcher and Dennis Amiss
Dennis Amiss and Fletcher's 176-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 125 between Dennis Amiss and Fletcher
Mike Denness and Chris Old's 89-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 59 between Fletcher and Tony Greig
Gavaskar and Gaekwad's 29-run partnership is IND's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Sudhir Naik and Gopal Bose
Viswanath and Gavaskar's 58-run partnership is IND's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 12 between Ajit Wadekar and Gopal Bose
Dennis Amiss and Fletcher's 176-run partnership is the highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 143 between Alvin Kallicharran and Fredericks
